{
    "no": 80,
    "name": "سُورَةُ عَبَسَ",
    "enName": "Abasa",
    "enNameTranslation": "He frowned",
    "bnNameTranslation": "আবাসা",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 42,
    "verses": [
        {
            "text": "عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",
            "bnText": "তিনি ভ্রূকুঞ্চিত করলেন এবং মুখ ফিরিয়ে নিলেন।",
            "enText": "The Prophet frowned and turned away",
            "enTextTransliteration": "'Abasa wa tawallaa.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5759",
            "numberInSurah": 1
        },
        {
            "text": "أَن جَاءَهُ الْأَعْمَىٰ",
            "bnText": "কারণ, তাঁর কাছে এক অন্ধ আগমন করল।",
            "enText": "Because there came to him the blind man, [interrupting].",
            "enTextTransliteration": "An jaa-ahul 'a-maa",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5760",
            "numberInSurah": 2
        },
        {
            "text": "وَمَا يُدْرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُ يَزَّكَّىٰ",
            "bnText": "আপনি কি জানেন, সে হয়তো পরিশুদ্ধ হত",
            "enText": "But what would make you perceive, [O Muhammad], that perhaps he might be purified",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa maa yudreeka la'allahu yaz zakkaa.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5761",
            "numberInSurah": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "أَوْ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ الذِّكْرَىٰ",
            "bnText": "অথবা উপদেশ গ্রহণ করতো এবং উপদেশ তার উপকার হত।",
            "enText": "Or be reminded and the remembrance would benefit him?",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Au yaz zak karu fatanfa 'ahuz zikraa.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5762",
            "numberInSurah": 4
        },
        {
            "text": "أَمَّا مَنِ اسْتَغْنَىٰ",
            "bnText": "পরন্তু যে বেপরোয়া",
            "enText": "As for he who thinks himself without need,",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Amma manis taghnaa",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5763",
            "numberInSurah": 5
        },
        {
            "text": "فَأَنتَ لَهُ تَصَدَّىٰ",
            "bnText": "আপনি তার চিন্তায় মশগুল।",
            "enText": "To him you give attention.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Fa-anta lahu tasaddaa",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5764",
            "numberInSurah": 6
        },
        {
            "text": "وَمَا عَلَيْكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ",
            "bnText": "সে শুদ্ধ না হলে আপনার কোন দোষ নেই।",
            "enText": "And not upon you [is any blame] if he will not be purified.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa ma 'alaika allaa yaz zakka.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5765",
            "numberInSurah": 7
        },
        {
            "text": "وَأَمَّا مَن جَاءَكَ يَسْعَىٰ",
            "bnText": "যে আপনার কাছে দৌড়ে আসলো",
            "enText": "But as for he who came to you striving [for knowledge]",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa amma man jaa-aka yas'a",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5766",
            "numberInSurah": 8
        },
        {
            "text": "وَهُوَ يَخْشَىٰ",
            "bnText": "এমতাবস্থায় যে, সে ভয় করে",
            "enText": "While he fears [Allah],",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wahuwa yakhshaa,",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5767",
            "numberInSurah": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "فَأَنتَ عَنْهُ تَلَهَّىٰ",
            "bnText": "আপনি তাকে অবজ্ঞা করলেন।",
            "enText": "From him you are distracted.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Fa-anta 'anhu talah haa.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5768",
            "numberInSurah": 10
        },
        {
            "text": "كَلَّا إِنَّهَا تَذْكِرَةٌ",
            "bnText": "কখনও এরূপ করবেন না, এটা উপদেশবানী।",
            "enText": "No! Indeed, these verses are a reminder;",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Kalla innaha tazkirah",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5769",
            "numberInSurah": 11
        },
        {
            "text": "فَمَن شَاءَ ذَكَرَهُ",
            "bnText": "অতএব, যে ইচ্ছা করবে, সে একে গ্রহণ করবে।",
            "enText": "So whoever wills may remember it.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Faman shaa a zakarah",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5770",
            "numberInSurah": 12
        },
        {
            "text": "فِي صُحُفٍ مُّكَرَّمَةٍ",
            "bnText": "এটা লিখিত আছে সম্মানিত",
            "enText": "[It is recorded] in honored sheets,",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Fi suhufim mukar rama,",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5771",
            "numberInSurah": 13
        },
        {
            "text": "مَّرْفُوعَةٍ مُّطَهَّرَةٍ",
            "bnText": "উচ্চ পবিত্র পত্রসমূহে",
            "enText": "Exalted and purified,",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Marfoo'atim mutah hara,",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5772",
            "numberInSurah": 14
        },
        {
            "text": "بِأَيْدِي سَفَرَةٍ",
            "bnText": "লিপিকারের হস্তে",
            "enText": "[Carried] by the hands of messenger-angels,",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Bi'aidee safara",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5773",
            "numberInSurah": 15
        },
        {
            "text": "كِرَامٍ بَرَرَةٍ",
            "bnText": "যারা মহৎ, পূত চরিত্র।",
            "enText": "Noble and dutiful.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Kiraamim bararah.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5774",
            "numberInSurah": 16
        },
        {
            "text": "قُتِلَ الْإِنسَانُ مَا أَكْفَرَهُ",
            "bnText": "মানুষ ধ্বংস হোক, সে কত অকৃতজ্ঞ",
            "enText": "Cursed is man; how disbelieving is he.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Qutilal-insanu maa akfarah.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5775",
            "numberInSurah": 17
        },
        {
            "text": "مِنْ أَيِّ شَيْءٍ خَلَقَهُ",
            "bnText": "তিনি তাকে কি বস্তু থেকে সৃষ্টি করেছেন",
            "enText": "From what substance did He create him?",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Min aiyyi shai-in Khalaq",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5776",
            "numberInSurah": 18
        },
        {
            "text": "مِن نُّطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُ فَقَدَّرَهُ",
            "bnText": "শুক্র থেকে তাকে সৃষ্টি করেছেন, অতঃপর তাকে সুপরিমিত করেছেন।",
            "enText": "From a sperm-drop He created him and destined for him;",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Min nutfah; khalaqahu faqad-darah.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5777",
            "numberInSurah": 19
        },
        {
            "text": "ثُمَّ السَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُ",
            "bnText": "অতঃপর তার পথ সহজ করেছেন",
            "enText": "Then He eased the way for him;",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Thummas sabeela yas-sarah",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5778",
            "numberInSurah": 20
        },
        {
            "text": "ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُ فَأَقْبَرَهُ",
            "bnText": "অতঃপর তার মৃত্যু ঘটান ও কবরস্থ করেন তাকে।",
            "enText": "Then He causes his death and provides a grave for him.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Thumma amatahu fa-aqbarah",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5779",
            "numberInSurah": 21
        },
        {
            "text": "ثُمَّ إِذَا شَاءَ أَنشَرَهُ",
            "bnText": "এরপর যখন ইচ্ছা করবেন তখন তাকে পুনরুজ্জীবিত করবেন।",
            "enText": "Then when He wills, He will resurrect him.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Thumma iza shaa-a ansharah",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5780",
            "numberInSurah": 22
        },
        {
            "text": "كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقْضِ مَا أَمَرَهُ",
            "bnText": "সে কখনও কৃতজ্ঞ হয়নি, তিনি তাকে যা আদেশ করেছেন, সে তা পূর্ণ করেনি।",
            "enText": "No! Man has not yet accomplished what He commanded him.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Kalla lamma yaqdi maa amarah.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5781",
            "numberInSurah": 23
        },
        {
            "text": "فَلْيَنظُرِ الْإِنسَانُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِ",
            "bnText": "মানুষ তার খাদ্যের প্রতি লক্ষ্য করুক",
            "enText": "Then let mankind look at his food -",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Falyanzuril insanu ilaa ta-amih",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5782",
            "numberInSurah": 24
        },
        {
            "text": "أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا الْمَاءَ صَبًّا",
            "bnText": "আমি আশ্চর্য উপায়ে পানি বর্ষণ করেছি",
            "enText": "How We poured down water in torrents,",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Anna sabab nalmaa-a sabba.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5783",
            "numberInSurah": 25
        },
        {
            "text": "ثُمَّ شَقَقْنَا الْأَرْضَ شَقًّا",
            "bnText": "এরপর আমি ভূমিকে বিদীর্ণ করেছি",
            "enText": "Then We broke open the earth, splitting [it with sprouts],",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Thumma sha qaqnal-arda shaqqa.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5784",
            "numberInSurah": 26
        },
        {
            "text": "فَأَنبَتْنَا فِيهَا حَبًّا",
            "bnText": "অতঃপর তাতে উৎপন্ন করেছি শস্য",
            "enText": "And caused to grow within it grain",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Fa ambatna feeha habba",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5785",
            "numberInSurah": 27
        },
        {
            "text": "وَعِنَبًا وَقَضْبًا",
            "bnText": "আঙ্গুর, শাক-সব্জি",
            "enText": "And grapes and herbage",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa 'inabaw-wa qadba",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5786",
            "numberInSurah": 28
        },
        {
            "text": "وَزَيْتُونًا وَنَخْلًا",
            "bnText": "যয়তুন, খর্জূর",
            "enText": "And olive and palm trees",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa zaitoonaw wanakh la'",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5787",
            "numberInSurah": 29
        },
        {
            "text": "وَحَدَائِقَ غُلْبًا",
            "bnText": "ঘন উদ্যান",
            "enText": "And gardens of dense shrubbery",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa hadaa-iqa ghulba",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5788",
            "numberInSurah": 30
        },
        {
            "text": "وَفَاكِهَةً وَأَبًّا",
            "bnText": "ফল এবং ঘাস",
            "enText": "And fruit and grass -",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa faki hataw-wa abba.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5789",
            "numberInSurah": 31
        },
        {
            "text": "مَّتَاعًا لَّكُمْ وَلِأَنْعَامِكُمْ",
            "bnText": "তোমাদেরও তোমাদের চতুস্পদ জন্তুদের উপাকারার্থে।",
            "enText": "[As] enjoyment for you and your grazing livestock.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Mata'al-lakum wa li-an'amikum.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5790",
            "numberInSurah": 32
        },
        {
            "text": "فَإِذَا جَاءَتِ الصَّاخَّةُ",
            "bnText": "অতঃপর যেদিন কর্ণবিদারক নাদ আসবে",
            "enText": "But when there comes the Deafening Blast",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Faiza jaa-atis saakhah.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5791",
            "numberInSurah": 33
        },
        {
            "text": "يَوْمَ يَفِرُّ الْمَرْءُ مِنْ أَخِيهِ",
            "bnText": "সেদিন পলায়ন করবে মানুষ তার ভ্রাতার কাছ থেকে",
            "enText": "On the Day a man will flee from his brother",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Yauma yafir-rul mar-u min akheeh",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5792",
            "numberInSurah": 34
        },
        {
            "text": "وَأُمِّهِ وَأَبِيهِ",
            "bnText": "তার মাতা, তার পিতা",
            "enText": "And his mother and his father",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa ummihee wa abeeh",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5793",
            "numberInSurah": 35
        },
        {
            "text": "وَصَاحِبَتِهِ وَبَنِيهِ",
            "bnText": "তার পত্নী ও তার সন্তানদের কাছ থেকে।",
            "enText": "And his wife and his children,",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa sahi batihee wa baneeh.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5794",
            "numberInSurah": 36
        },
        {
            "text": "لِكُلِّ امْرِئٍ مِّنْهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ شَأْنٌ يُغْنِيهِ",
            "bnText": "সেদিন প্রত্যেকেরই নিজের এক চিন্তা থাকবে, যা তাকে ব্যতিব্যস্ত করে রাখবে।",
            "enText": "For every man, that Day, will be a matter adequate for him.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Likul limri-im-minuhm yaumaa-izin shaa nuy-yughneeh",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5795",
            "numberInSurah": 37
        },
        {
            "text": "وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ مُّسْفِرَةٌ",
            "bnText": "অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে উজ্জ্বল",
            "enText": "[Some] faces, that Day, will be bright -",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wujoo huny-yauma-izim-musfira;",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5796",
            "numberInSurah": 38
        },
        {
            "text": "ضَاحِكَةٌ مُّسْتَبْشِرَةٌ",
            "bnText": "সহাস্য ও প্রফুল্ল।",
            "enText": "Laughing, rejoicing at good news.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Dahi katum mustab shirah",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5797",
            "numberInSurah": 39
        },
        {
            "text": "وَوُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ عَلَيْهَا غَبَرَةٌ",
            "bnText": "এবং অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে ধুলি ধূসরিত।",
            "enText": "And [other] faces, that Day, will have upon them dust.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Wa wujoohuy yauma-izin 'alaiha ghabar a",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5798",
            "numberInSurah": 40
        },
        {
            "text": "تَرْهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ",
            "bnText": "তাদেরকে কালিমা আচ্ছন্ন করে রাখবে।",
            "enText": "Blackness will cover them.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Tarhaquha qatarah.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5799",
            "numberInSurah": 41
        },
        {
            "text": "أُولَٰئِكَ هُمُ الْكَفَرَةُ الْفَجَرَةُ",
            "bnText": "তারাই কাফের পাপিষ্ঠের দল।",
            "enText": "Those are the disbelievers, the wicked ones.",
            "enTextTransliteration": "Ulaa-ika humul-kafa ratul-fajarah.",
            "audioPrimary": "https://cdn.alquran.cloud/media/audio/ayah/ar.alafasy/5800",
            "numberInSurah": 42
        }
    ]
}